pisode<br />\n今集真係神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTelltale 係整Walking dead 先有心機 ，<br />\nBatman ，games of thorn全部hea整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8228f2881796ed762e48845e8ca0f1ddfbbee2e0","tid":47122,"uid":1954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:28:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩完頭兩個episode<br />\n今集真係神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTelltale 係整Walking dead 先有心機 ，<br />\nBatman ，games of thorn全部hea整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今集睇得出telltale好有心機整，telltale 既the wolf among us 同 tales from the borderlands 都做得好好<br />\n但係walking dead michonne 係垃圾，完全唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee02fa0ec67d3d69b1a3ccdfa728922f12e8520e","tid":47122,"uid":1954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實之前個兩集做既大決定對今集有冇影響<br />\n佢開頭有得自己組織返之前既決定<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">btw Kenny :(((((((( </span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">劇透！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">其實都估到season3入面一定會死哂season2剩底既角色<br />\n唔係既話支線咁多點整得哂<br />\n但我見到Kenny嗰個真係好嬲覺得好唔尊重依個角色 <br />\nJane個死法都好過佢多多聲<br />\n有唔少人因為咁 情願喺一開頭就話殺咗kenny算 至少咁樣嘅死有意義好多</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實上一集既大決定有少少少少有影響就係clem受傷位置，如果係alone ending會好似trailer咁斷左隻手指，即係telltale 預設都係想Clem 自己帶住AJ生活<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">Kenny都算係英雄式離場，Jane簡直由頭到尾都係自私撚，唔想關心對任何人，唔想負責任</span></span>"},{"pid":"f9b315ff944fa339a1d3bf5a2033545020151950","tid":47122,"uid":67596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實之前個兩集做既大決定對今集有冇影響<br />\n佢開頭有得自己組織返之前既決定<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">btw Kenny :(((((((( </span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">劇透！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">其實都估到season3入面一定會死哂season2剩底既角色<br />\n唔係既話支線咁多點整得哂<br />\n但我見到Kenny嗰個真係好嬲覺得好唔尊重依個角色 <br />\nJane個死法都好過佢多多聲<br />\n有唔少人因為咁 情願喺一開頭就話殺咗kenny算 至少咁樣嘅死有意義好多</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實上一集既大決定有少少少少有影響就係clem受傷位置，如果係alone ending會好似trailer咁斷左隻手指，即係telltale 預設都係想Clem 自己帶住AJ生活<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">Kenny都算係英雄式離場，Jane簡直由頭到尾都係自私撚，唔想關心對任何人，唔想負責任</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但只少都俾clem幫kenny快啲結束佢嘅痛苦都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 望住Kenny俾班屍抓同咬嗰下好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span><br />\n我覺得Jane其實係真係關心Clem 不過佢係想私有化佢 始終season2嘅角色development做得麻麻 Jane依個角色唔夠深入突顯佢嘅好 搞到好多人真係諗都唔洗諗一定揀Kenny 在我立場我唔係好中意season 2堆人 Luke,Jane除外<br />\nSarah,Rebecca嗰堆真係負累嚟 煩撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28b51f491ed1b970f23425a6e4c52aa2ba109ea","tid":47122,"uid":28812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:21:01.000Z","msg":"繼續推<br />\n推到出episode 3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed67a5fddab4e22b2ecef8db948f3d732a29ac9","tid":47122,"uid":1954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>繼續推<br />\n推到出episode 3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n變左劇情討論post <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f75c36bca2dc2d2f880ce6977ca0abca1c08196","tid":47122,"uid":1954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:00:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">劇透！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">其實都估到season3入面一定會死哂season2剩底既角色<br />\n唔係既話支線咁多點整得哂<br />\n但我見到Kenny嗰個真係好嬲覺得好唔尊重依個角色 <br />\nJane個死法都好過佢多多聲<br />\n有唔少人因為咁 情願喺一開頭就話殺咗kenny算 至少咁樣嘅死有意義好多</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實上一集既大決定有少少少少有影響就係clem受傷位置，如果係alone ending會好似trailer咁斷左隻手指，即係telltale 預設都係想Clem 自己帶住AJ生活<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">Kenny都算係英雄式離場，Jane簡直由頭到尾都係自私撚，唔想關心對任何人，唔想負責任</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但只少都俾clem幫kenny快啲結束佢嘅痛苦都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 望住Kenny俾班屍抓同咬嗰下好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span><br />\n我覺得Jane其實係真係關心Clem 不過佢係想私有化佢 始終season2嘅角色development做得麻麻 Jane依個角色唔夠深入突顯佢嘅好 搞到好多人真係諗都唔洗諗一定揀Kenny 在我立場我唔係好中意season 2堆人 Luke,Jane除外<br />\nSarah,Rebecca嗰堆真係負累嚟 煩撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nKenny 都話咩都feel唔到就無謂浪費子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我對jane真係冇乜好感，佢係想將clem私有化，似係想用黎代替佢個妹咁，但同時佢盡量唔想關心人，怕受傷<br />\n我認同你話Season 2同（同埋michonne）既角色都好煩膠 死左都冇咩感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69cf0cdf9da1eaac02ccb3a47f99e17c01d85319","tid":47122,"uid":67596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實上一集既大決定有少少少少有影響就係clem受傷位置，如果係alone ending會好似trailer咁斷左隻手指，即係telltale 預設都係想Clem 自己帶住AJ生活<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">Kenny都算係英雄式離場，Jane簡直由頭到尾都係自私撚，唔想關心對任何人，唔想負責任</span></span></blockquote><br /